com.wx.action.arg

Interface ArgumentsSupplier

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CombinedSupplier, ObjectsSupplier

    public interface ArgumentsSupplier
    Interface that represents an iterator of arguments. An object of this instance contains an ordered list of arguments. These arguments can be iterated using the right method according to the type of the next argument. The behaviour of calling the method corresponding to the wrong type depends on the implementation.

    Created on 19/11/2014
